        <!-- How Work Content Start -->
        <div class="how-work-content">
          <!-- Section Title Start -->
          <div class="section-title">
            <h3 class="wow fadeInUp">Your Physiotherapy FAQs</h3>
            <h2 class="text-anime-style-3" data-cursor="-opaque">
              Have Questions?
            </h2>
          </div>
          <!-- Section Title End -->

          <!-- How Work Accordion Start -->
          <div class="how-work-accordion" id="accordion">
            <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading1">
                <span class="icon-box">
                  <img src="images/icon-how-it-work-1.svg" alt="" />
                </span>
                <button
                  class="accordion-button"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapse1"
                  aria-expanded="true"
                  aria-controls="collapse1"
                >
                  What should I expect during my first visit?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapse1"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse show"
                aria-labelledby="heading1"
                data-bs-parent="#accordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>
                    Your first visit with Dr. Heli Gandhi involves a
                    comprehensive assessment to understand your condition and
                    health goals. We will discuss your history, perform a
                    physical evaluation, and develop a personalized treatment
                    plan to start your recovery.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.25s">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading2">
                <span class="icon-box">
                  <img src="images/icon-how-it-work-2.svg" alt="" />
                </span>
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapse2"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapse2"
                >
                  What conditions do you treat?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapse2"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                aria-labelledby="heading2"
                data-bs-parent="#accordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>
                    We treat a wide range of issues, including Orthopaedic
                    (musculoskeletal) pain, sports injuries, and neurological
                    disorders. We also offer specialized Pediatric physio,
                    Manual Therapy, and programs for Urinary Incontinence,
                    Weight Loss, and Dysphasia.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.5s">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading3">
                <span class="icon-box">
                  <img src="images/icon-how-it-work-2.svg" alt="" />
                </span>
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapse3"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapse3"
                >
                  What is Manual Therapy?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapse3"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                aria-labelledby="heading3"
                data-bs-parent="#accordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>
                    Manual Therapy is a specialized, hands-on treatment where
                    the physiotherapist uses skilled hand movements to mobilize
                    joints and soft tissue. It is highly effective for reducing
                    pain, decreasing stiffness, and improving your range of
                    motion.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="accordion-item wow fadeInUp" data-wow-delay="0.75s">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="heading4">
                <span class="icon-box">
                  <img src="images/icon-how-it-work-4.svg" alt="" />
                </span>
                <button
                  class="accordion-button collapsed"
                  type="button"
                  data-bs-toggle="collapse"
                  data-bs-target="#collapse4"
                  aria-expanded="false"
                  aria-controls="collapse4"
                >
                  Do I need a doctor's referral to book an appointment?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div
                id="collapse4"
                class="accordion-collapse collapse"
                aria-labelledby="heading4"
                data-bs-parent="#accordion"
              >
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  <p>
                    No, you do not need a doctor's referral to book an
                    appointment with us. You can contact our Ahmedabad clinic
                    directly to schedule your assessment. We will conduct a full
                    evaluation and, if necessary, coordinate with your doctor.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
